<li id="lithub_daily_widget-9" class="widget widget_lithub_daily_widget"><div class="lithub-daily-header"><a href="/category/lit-hub-daily/"><b>Lithub</b> Daily</a></div><h2 class="widgettitle">January 2, 2025</h2>
<a href="https://lithub.com/lit-hub-daily-january-2-2025/"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-247643 size-thumbnail" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2024-12-20-at-4.12.28 PM-150x150.png" alt="baseball" width="150" height="150" /></a>
<ul>
 	<li><a href="https://www.nplusonemag.com/online-only/online-only/this-fall-in-baseball/" class="external" target="_blank"><span style="font-weight: 400">Some thoughts about baseball</span></a></li>
 	<li><a href="https://daily.jstor.org/rosemary-the-herb-of-ritual-and-remembrance/" class="external" target="_blank"><span style="font-weight: 400">The fragrant history of rosemary</span></a></li>
 	<li><a href="https://harpers.org/archive/2025/01/voices-from-the-dead-letter-office-cynthia-ozick-epistolary-life/" class="external" target="_blank"><span style="font-weight: 400">A eulogy for letter writing</span></a></li>
